<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Thu, 25 Jul 2024 14:07:25 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>以色列军队报告三名以色列国防军士兵在约旦河西岸高速公路枪击事件中受伤</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-25/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-reports-three-idf-soldiers-wounded-in-west-bank-highway-shooting/00000190-e9a5-d298-a592-f9b7ebf60000</link><description>士兵们在绿线西岸城市盖勒吉利亚附近的 55 号高速公路上行驶时被枪杀。士兵们的情况为中度和轻症，被疏散到卡法萨巴的梅尔医院。军方表示，目前正在搜寻枪手</description><pubDate>Thu, 25 Jul 2024 12:23:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-25/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-reports-three-idf-soldiers-wounded-in-west-bank-highway-shooting/00000190-e9a5-d298-a592-f9b7ebf60000</guid></item><item><title>以色列政府敦促最高法院驳回巴勒斯坦权力机构针对恐怖受害者赔偿法的请愿书</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-25/ty-article/.premium/israeli-govt-urges-top-court-to-reject-pa-petition-against-terror-victim-compensation-law/00000190-e95e-d8b8-a59a-edde2fd00000</link><description>7月初，巴勒斯坦权力机构首次向以色列法院提出请愿，要求以色列法院驳回允许恐怖袭击受害者起诉巴勒斯坦权力机构要求赔偿的以色列议会法律。以色列政府要求法院驳回请愿书，称巴勒斯坦权力机构向恐怖分子及其家人支付报酬</description><pubDate>Thu, 25 Jul 2024 12:12:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-25/ty-article/.premium/israeli-govt-urges-top-court-to-reject-pa-petition-against-terror-victim-compensation-law/00000190-e95e-d8b8-a59a-edde2fd00000</guid></item><item><title>最高法院声明：解释为何本格维尔部的非法枪支许可证尚未被取消</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-25/ty-article/.premium/top-court-to-state-explain-why-ben-gvirs-illegal-gun-licenses-havent-been-annulled/00000190-e8fe-d8b8-a59a-ecfe0aa10000</link><description>以色列高等法院正在审理一份请愿书，要求废除 12,000 多张枪支许可证，因为本-格维尔的部门显然没有遵循程序并非法发放枪支许可证</description><pubDate>Thu, 25 Jul 2024 11:19:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-25/ty-article/.premium/top-court-to-state-explain-why-ben-gvirs-illegal-gun-licenses-havent-been-annulled/00000190-e8fe-d8b8-a59a-ecfe0aa10000</guid></item><item><title>本-格维尔在联盟协议中控制了西岸非法建设执法</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-25/ty-article/.premium/ben-gvir-gets-control-over-illegal-west-bank-construction-enforcement-in-coalition-deal/00000190-e8e1-d603-abb5-f9e3d36d0000</link><description>在正统派和本格维尔就另一项授权拉比理事会有权使用手机的法律达成协议后，以色列议会通过了这项将权力从斯莫特里奇转移到本格维尔的法律。</description><pubDate>Thu, 25 Jul 2024 10:51:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-25/ty-article/.premium/ben-gvir-gets-control-over-illegal-west-bank-construction-enforcement-in-coalition-deal/00000190-e8e1-d603-abb5-f9e3d36d0000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡将于周四会见拜登和哈里斯，因为美国要求结束加沙战争的压力越来越大</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-25/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-will-meet-biden-harris-on-thursday-amid-mounting-u-s-pressure-to-end-gaza-war/00000190-e921-d8b8-a59a-edbf12f00000</link><description>人质家属预计将出席白宫会议。除了释放人质的努力外，美国还向内塔尼亚胡寻求有关停止战斗和加沙战后计划的最新信息。内塔尼亚胡周五还将在特朗普位于佛罗里达州的庄园会见特朗普</description><pubDate>Thu, 25 Jul 2024 09:51:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-25/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-will-meet-biden-harris-on-thursday-amid-mounting-u-s-pressure-to-end-gaza-war/00000190-e921-d8b8-a59a-edbf12f00000</guid></item><item><title>澳大利亚制裁参与西岸针对巴勒斯坦人的暴力行为的七名以色列定居者</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-25/ty-article/.premium/australia-sanctions-seven-israelis-involved-in-west-bank-violence-against-palestinians/00000190-e8ba-d469-a39d-ecbfc0310000</link><description>澳大利亚的声明称，一些以色列人参与了性侵犯和性虐待。制裁还针对“山顶青年”，此举将使未来能够对参与袭击巴勒斯坦人的非法前哨定居者采取更广泛的行动</description><pubDate>Thu, 25 Jul 2024 07:57:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-25/ty-article/.premium/australia-sanctions-seven-israelis-involved-in-west-bank-violence-against-palestinians/00000190-e8ba-d469-a39d-ecbfc0310000</guid></item><item><title>全文：内塔尼亚胡 2024 年向国会发表的讲话</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-25/ty-article/full-text-netanyahus-2024-address-to-congress/00000190-e6c0-d469-a39d-e6d7117d0000</link><description></description><pubDate>Thu, 25 Jul 2024 07:34:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-25/ty-article/full-text-netanyahus-2024-address-to-congress/00000190-e6c0-d469-a39d-e6d7117d0000</guid></item><item><title>如果加沙没有最终结果并脱离现实，内塔尼亚胡的雄辩无法赢得对以色列的支持</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-25/ty-article/.premium/without-a-gaza-endgame-netanyahus-eloquence-wont-translate-into-support-for-israel/00000190-e688-db2f-a3b3-fefec4ad0000</link><description>如果内塔尼亚胡声称人质的命运如此紧迫，他就不会再次推迟卡塔尔谈判的恢复；与总理关系密切的人士称他的讲话具有历史意义，但以色列人专注于救回人质，而美国人则专注于选举</description><pubDate>Thu, 25 Jul 2024 03:03:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-25/ty-article/.premium/without-a-gaza-endgame-netanyahus-eloquence-wont-translate-into-support-for-israel/00000190-e688-db2f-a3b3-fefec4ad0000</guid></item><item><title>特朗普在内塔尼亚胡会议之前表示，以色列必须“快速”结束加沙战争，归还人质</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-25/ty-article-live/gaza-truce-talks-in-closing-stages-senior-u-s-official-says-israeli-source-gaps-remain/00000190-e7ae-d469-a39d-e7bfcb150000</link><description>据报道，英国将撤回对国际刑事法院逮捕内塔尼亚胡、加兰特的反对意见 ■ 以色列国防军：三名士兵在约旦河西岸枪击事件中受伤 ■ 以色列国防军找到了 10 月 7 日被杀并被带到加沙的五名以色列人的尸体 ■ 在美国压力越来越大的情况下，内塔尼亚胡会见拜登和哈里斯结束加沙战争 ■ 以色列推迟卡塔尔会谈；官员表示，等待拜登和内塔尼亚胡就加沙协议进行讨论后离开</description><pubDate>Thu, 25 Jul 2024 02:28:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-25/ty-article-live/gaza-truce-talks-in-closing-stages-senior-u-s-official-says-israeli-source-gaps-remain/00000190-e7ae-d469-a39d-e7bfcb150000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡在国会的空洞“胜利”：在演讲中获胜，在战争中失败</titl