-d8b8-a59a-eede01260000</link><description>以色列军队表示，本周在汗尤尼斯发动的袭击（据报道有 70 名巴勒斯坦人被杀）的主要目标之一是打捞人质的尸体</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Jul 2024 20:16:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-24/ty-article/israel-recovers-body-of-maya-goren-kidnapped-on-oct-7-and-killed-in-captivity/00000190-e656-d8b8-a59a-eede01260000</guid></item><item><title>本-格维尔推动立法让他控制以色列国民警卫队</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-24/ty-article/.premium/ben-gvir-pushes-legislation-giving-him-control-over-israels-national-guard/00000190-e55c-d149-afbb-ef5dc7080000</link><description>一位知情人士告诉《国土报》，极右翼国家安全部长的决议草案“试图建立一支由他控制的安全部队”</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Jul 2024 19:49:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-24/ty-article/.premium/ben-gvir-pushes-legislation-giving-him-control-over-israels-national-guard/00000190-e55c-d149-afbb-ef5dc7080000</guid></item><item><title>以色列推迟卡塔尔会谈；官员表示，等待拜登和内塔尼亚胡就加沙协议进行讨论后离开</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-24/ty-article/.premium/israel-delays-qatar-talks-departure-awaits-biden-netanyahu-discussion-on-gaza-deal/00000190-e5c9-d322-a1df-efff518b0000</link><description>一名官员表示，拜登和内塔尼亚胡之间的会面对于设定人质交易的参数至关重要 ■ 人质的母亲指责总理出于个人利益而阻止交易</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Jul 2024 17:54:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-24/ty-article/.premium/israel-delays-qatar-talks-departure-awaits-biden-netanyahu-discussion-on-gaza-deal/00000190-e5c9-d322-a1df-efff518b0000</guid></item><item><title>“内塔尼亚胡是战犯”：以色列总理在国会发表讲话，数千人在美国国会大厦外抗议</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-07-24/ty-article/.premium/thousands-protest-outside-u-s-capitol-as-israeli-pm-addresses-congress/00000190-e5c1-d149-afbb-efc5bd570000</link><description>在内塔尼亚胡总理向国会发表讲话之前，已部署了大量警察部队。早些时候，示威者试图阻止以色列总理前往国会山的车队，并在他的酒店外悬挂巴勒斯坦国旗</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Jul 2024 17:53:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-07-24/ty-article/.premium/thousands-protest-outside-u-s-capitol-as-israeli-pm-addresses-congress/00000190-e5c1-d149-afbb-efc5bd570000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡会见美国福音派领袖，称以色列“没有更好的朋友”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-07-24/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-meets-u-s-evangelical-leaders-says-israel-has-no-better-friends/00000190-e5af-d322-a1df-efff46170000</link><description>以色列总理会见了几位信仰领袖，其中包括约翰·哈吉牧师，他在活动中表示基督徒“对我们政府对待犹太人民的方式感到震惊”</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Jul 2024 17:41:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-07-24/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-meets-u-s-evangelical-leaders-says-israel-has-no-better-friends/00000190-e5af-d322-a1df-efff46170000</guid></item><item><title>以色列处于战争状态，第 292 天：甘茨说，自上次休战提议以来，四分之一的活着的人质死亡</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-24/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-292-quarter-of-hostages-died-since-last-truce-proposal-gantz-says/00000190-e5ad-d322-a1df-efff0d3d0001</link><description>总理内塔尼亚胡在国会联席会议上发表讲话，反对议员的强烈抗议和抵制 ■ 以色列将原定于周四前往卡塔尔的代表团推迟到下周 ■ 以色列将 250 名加沙伤病员疏散到阿联酋接受治疗 ■ 真主党发布了以色列人的无人机镜头空军基地 ■ 战争进入 292 天后，您需要了解以下内容</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Jul 2024 17:03:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-24/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-292-quarter-of-hostages-died-since-last-truce-proposal-gantz-says/00000190-e5ad-d322-a1df-efff0d3d0001</guid></item><item><title>100年前想要皈依犹太教的贝都因部落后来怎么样了？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-24/ty-article/.premium/what-had-happened-to-the-bedouin-tribe-that-wanted-to-convert-to-judaism-100-years-ago/00000190-e49c-dab4-afb9-f7fcf7e60000</link><description>整整一个世纪前，《国土报》报道了加利利的一个部落寻求皈依。 1948年犹太人就是这样对待它的</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Jul 2024 16:06:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-24/ty-article/.premium/what-had-happened-to-the-bedouin-tribe-that-wanted-to-convert-to-judaism-100-years-ago/00000190-e49c-dab4-afb9-f7fcf7e60000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡即将在国会发表讲话，他面临着最可怕的噩梦：无关紧要</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-07-24/ty-article/.premium/set-to-address-congress-netanyahu-faces-his-worst-nightmare-irrelevancy/00000190-e425-d363-abbf-eeaf81ca0000</link><description>总理本打算将内塔尼亚胡的讲话视为美以关系的里程碑时刻，但内塔尼亚胡的讲话将被深深分裂、有些敌对、几乎完全心烦意乱的听众听到</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Jul 2024 14:47:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-07-24/ty-article/.premium/set-to-address-congress-netanyahu-faces-his-worst-nightmare-irrelevancy/00000190-e425-d363-abbf-eeaf81ca0000</guid></item></channel></rss>